Class AeWSDLSchemaResolver

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
org.exolab.castor.net.URIResolver
public class AeWSDLSchemaResolver
extends AeURIResolver

The WSDL Schema resolver class is used to resolve schemas within a single WSDL file. It is possible to construct a WSDL file with multiple <schema> elements, each with different target namespaces. This resolver is used when one of these schemas tries to import one of the other schemas in the same WSDL. This is done by using a schema <import> element with a namespace attribute but no schemaLocation attribute.
